Non-commercial use only, or ask for permission first.

Commercial use includes (but is not limited to):
- SAAD (sauna-as-a-device): selling saunas fitted with this software, retrofitting saunas with this software, selling hardware that includes this software
- SAAS (sauna-as-a-service): providing access to a sauna fitted with this software following an agreement of goods or service exchange (ie. you're not allowed to tell a friend "bring beer and I'll provide the sauna" ; the friend should be free to bring beer or any other drink they say fit, if they see fit, whenever they see fit, UNLESS the total amount of good and services for the sauna session does not exceed the running costs of that sauna session ie. "each participants may be asked to contribute with a portion of the kWh required for the session")
